In this lecture, we are going to learn Chinese culture by studying Chinese people’s social customs and habits.We are also going to learn the basics about Chinese language and have discussions on the differences between the Chinese culture and Japanese culture. This lecture is going to help to develop your Chinese language abilities including listening ability, writing ability and conversation ability.
